Programming new feature process:
1. Understand business requirements and business goal
1.1 If there is anything confusing or breaking current state, talk about it before going further
2. If you failed at step 1, go back to step 1
3. Understand how this new feature impacts the system
4. Think and plan implementation
5. Start writing code
5.1 Remember about tests ;)
6. Perform tests
7. Create pull-request
7.1 Keep correcting code and talking about this PR untill every comment is resolved and PR is approved by other team member(s)
8. Close PR and let CI pipeline do it's job